Language: <F P=105> Arabic </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Excerpt] The Presidential Council held a meeting under 
brother Lieutenant General 'Ali 'Abdallah Salih, Presidential 
Council chairman, today. During the meeting, the council 
discussed many issues and developments on the national, Arab, 
and international scene. The Presidential Council also examined 
the national situation in light of the overall developments on 
the national scene. It instructed the government to motivate 
the state's departments, institutions, and administrations to 
overcome the state of inactivity that has prevailed in them in 
light of the political crisis and its effects on their work and 
performance. [passage omitted] 

